name: Senior #10 - Pablo
description:
Although the cause of death was reported as cancer, Pablo, a 62-year-old successful senior politician, is convinced that his half sister, Nkosi, was murdered.

He defines himself as asexual. He has a postgraduate degree in philosophy, politics, economics and kinesiology.

Pablo grew up in a middle class neighbourhood. Having never really known his parents, he was raised in a series of foster homes.
